# ============================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# ============================================
#
# Problem: Firebase not connecting
# Solution: 
#   - Verify all REACT_APP_FIREBASE_* variables are correct
#   - Check Firebase Console → Project Settings
#   - Ensure project is on Blaze plan (required for Cloud Functions)
#
# Problem: PayPal errors
# Solution:
#   - Verify REACT_APP_PAYPAL_CLIENT_ID_PROD is correct
#   - Check PayPal Business account is verified
#   - Test in sandbox first with REACT_APP_PAYPAL_CLIENT_ID_SANDBOX
#   - Check browser console for specific error messages
#
# Problem: Emails not sending
# Solution:
#   - Verify all REACT_APP_EMAILJS_* variables are correct
#   - Check EmailJS Dashboard → Service status
#   - Verify email service (Gmail/Outlook) is connected
#   - Check EmailJS monthly quota (free tier: 200 emails/month)
#
# Problem: Environment variables not updating
# Solution:
#   - Vercel: Redeploy after changing variables
#   - Local: Restart dev server (npm start)
#   - Clear browser cache
#   - Check variable names match exactly (case-sensitive)
#
# Problem: Build fails on Vercel
# Solution:
#   - Check all required variables are set
#   - Ensure NODE_ENV=production
#   - Check Vercel build logs for specific error
#   - Verify package.json dependencies are correct
#
# ============================================


